node.text:
As we hope to start a family one day, we know that family planning is so important. Half of fertility issues involve male-factor issues and it is important to identify and implement lifestyle modifications that can aid in the success of a healthy pregnancy.

Legacy is a digital fertility clinic that allows you to test, freeze, and improve your sperm from home. They’re making male fertility more approachable, so men can be more proactive. A survey revealed that 73% of men who were thinking about or trying to start a family have no knowledge of their sperm quality. And all too often men's fertility isn't tested at all until a couple has been trying for 12 months, even though many male fertility issues can be fixed with simple lifestyle changes. Legacy had replaced the clinic with the comfort of home and put the power of proactive testing and data in your hands.

Legacy's digital-first clinic approach and affordable mail-in sperm testing make male fertility care available to more people than ever before. Legacy offers the most advanced mail-in semen analysis kit available. Legacy’s labs test and report the five key factors of sperm health, with options to assess sperm’s genetic health (DNA fragmentation) and to freeze your sample for use in the future. No other at-home semen testing kit offers sperm DNA fragmentation analysis.

Legacy gives you the tools to not only understand your fertility, but improve it. Every client gets an in-depth report of their sperm health along with personalized guidance for lifestyle changes that may improve their fertility, based on a comprehensive survey they completed. Additionally, all clients have the opportunity to discuss their results and their family goals with a Legacy male fertility expert.
Legacy prizes privacy and security. Client data is encrypted, and is HIPAA- , CCPA- & GDPR-compliant. No data is sold.
The Legacy team is a Harvard-backed group of people who understand parenthood—and how much it matters. The team brings international experience in fertility, health care policy, and business with a world-class advisory board.

#sponsored #protectyourlegacy, #preserveyourlegacy #givelegacy @givelegacyinc
